<p>At Scales Elder Law, we understand that when it comes to Medicaid planning, nursing home abuse, wills and trusts, and probate matters, your peace of mind depends on results. Our experienced attorneys have a strong track record of securing favorable outcomes for clients throughout the state, protecting their assets, rights, and dignity every step of the way.</p>
<p>Here are just a few examples of our recent case results that demonstrate our unwavering commitment and expertise:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Medicaid Planning Victory:</strong> Successfully helped a local family preserve over $150,000 in assets while qualifying their loved one for Medicaid long-term care benefits, ensuring quality care without financial devastation.</li>
  <li><strong>Nursing Home Abuse Settlement:</strong> Secured a six-figure settlement for a client who suffered neglect and abuse in a nursing facility, holding the responsible parties accountable and providing financial relief for medical expenses and emotional trauma.</li>
  <li><strong>Wills and Trusts Establishment:</strong> Guided multiple families through the creation of comprehensive wills and trusts that avoid probate, minimize estate taxes, and protect heirs from unnecessary legal complications.</li>
  <li><strong>Probate Case Success:</strong> Efficiently navigated a complex probate case involving contested wills, resulting in a favorable distribution of assets in accordance with the decedent’s wishes and state laws.</li>
</ul>
